twoSetSkill.name: Pateticheskaya 2 Pieces
twoSetSkill.description: After casting the Ultimate, next team member switching in gains a 10% Total DMG Multiplier buff (does not stack) for 10s. CD: 30s.

threeSetSkill.name: Zimniye Gryozy 3 Pieces
threeSetSkill.description: After casting the Ultimate, next team member switching in takes 30% less Total DMG (effect does not stack) for 10s and restores HP equal to 10% of the host's Max HP. CD: 30s.
